column5: LOL Bookoobeast! Carlton always killed me when he did his famous dance!

Thanks to all of you for your well wishes!   Shawn took me out to dinner last night and boy was it awesome! I picked Applebee's to eat at, and I could not have asked for a better dinner and we had a great time! I had the baby back rib dinner with a nice cold corona and Shawn had a steak dinner with a nice cold bud. Forget the fancy dinner and wine, that is MY kind of dinner.
